      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Bash your<strong> lemongrass stalk[s]</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until it splits open</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> bashed lemongrass</strong> and<strong> diced chicken breast</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 7-8 min or until lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683884133885-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
