          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683884133885-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683884133885-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683884133885-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683884133885-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and cut into quarters lengthwise – these are your<strong> lettuce wedges</strong></p><p>Roughly chop your<strong> roasted peanuts</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1720710227590-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1720710227590-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1720710227590-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
