          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1683884141267-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once lightly browned, add the<strong> tamarind sauce</strong> to the chicken and cook for a further 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> lime[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Once cooked through, add generous squeeze of<strong> lime juice </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>tamarind & lemongrass chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1683884146112-x200.jpg",
