            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped peanuts</strong> and the<strong> remaining honey</strong> in a bowl with a generous squeeze of<strong> lime juice</strong> (reserve some lime for a garnish!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> - this is your <strong>peanut & lime dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683884163923-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683884163923-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683884163923-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683884163923-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683884163923-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Discard the<strong> lemongrass stalk[s]</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>tamarind & lemongrass chicken </strong>over the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with the <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>lettuce wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>peanut & lime dressing</strong> over the carrot and wedges</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
